News Releases, Media Advisories

January 14, 2004

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
BATTLES FOR CONGRESS
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final report on Battles for Congress (RI 1st District). This audit covers the period of June 12, 2001 through December 31, 2002.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street NW
title: Final Audit Report on Battles for Congress is Now Available
